E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Alex Fletcher, Tisha Merry, Gemma Bissix, Charlie Wernham and Gary Lucy join Kieron Richardson for a deep dive into the world of Hollyoaks as it celebrates 30 years. (Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's rural retreat time, and a welcome romantic break for some. But rumours about a bride's behaviour spiral, and another bride learns a heartbreaking truth. (S10 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics have been watching The Masked Singer, Trigger Point, Pam & Tommy, First Dates: Valentine's, Mary Beard's Forgotten Art, and Dragons' Den. (S19 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Hollyoaks Later
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new: Hollyoaks Later collides with Brookside as residents escape the Close for Liverpool's luxury suburbs, where old secrets ignite new betrayals when a party turns deadly.

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Can meat-loving teacher Marie control her sledgehammer wit when she finds out that her date Davin is a vegan? Sexagenarians Lynda and Philip both like younger men. DJ Tom is back. (S7 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's rural retreat time, and a welcome romantic break for some. But rumours about a bride's behaviour spiral, and another bride learns a heartbreaking truth. (S10 Ep22) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks Later
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new: Hollyoaks Later collides with Brookside as residents escape the Close for Liverpool's luxury suburbs, where old secrets ignite new betrayals when a party turns deadly. [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Below Deck Sailing Yacht
E4Plus1.uk.description: Much Ado About Crushing: The fight for Chase's affection heats up. And the drama bubbles over as a wild night out in a hot tub ends with an unexpected bang. (S5 Ep11/16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart After Dark: Bart gets a job at a burlesque theatre. Several residents are keen customers, but others aren't happy to have the showgirls peddling their wares in Springfield. (S8 Ep5/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's the Great Pumpkin, Phil Dunphy: Phil and Claire want to celebrate Halloween in a big way, but no one else seems to share their enthusiasm for it. (S9 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Geology Methodology: Sheldon and Bert collaborate on a research project, but Sheldon feels embarrassed to be associated with the study of geology. (S11 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bitcoin Entanglement: Sheldon seeks revenge when the guys cut him out of a potentially valuable investment. A secret about Leonard and Penny is revealed. (S11 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Confidence Erosion: Sheldon and Amy try to use maths to make their wedding planning less stressful. Raj falls out with Howard. (S11 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Climb: Gemma decides to fire a teacher but isn't prepared for the aftermath. Calvin gets a surprise when he faces off with his paper boy. (S1 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Basketball!: Phil's been doing basketball training so that he can redeem himself at the annual charity game. Then NBA stars Charles Barkley and DeAndre Jordan turn up... (S8 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pig Moon Rising: Mitchell accidentally knocks over an urn filled with Cam's beloved pet pig Lilly's ashes. Can he cover up his blunder? (S8 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Michon's: Can Gordon help the unwell owner of a family-run Atlanta smokehouse address his daughter's hands-off management style? (S5 Ep11) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's rural retreat time, and a welcome romantic break for some. But rumours about a bride's behaviour spiral, and another bride learns a heartbreaking truth. (S10 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Last Tap Dance in Springfield: Lisa takes up dancing but discovers that she's not very good at it. Bart and Milhouse duck out of their camping trip and hide out in the mall. (S11 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's a Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad Marge: Otto's rock 'n' roll marriage to his girlfriend Becky (Parker Posey) is over as soon as it's begun. So Becky moves in with the Simpsons. (S11 Ep21/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Gorilla Dissolution: Penny re-evaluates her life, including taking a big step with Leonard, while Howard and Bernadette struggle to look after Mrs Wolowitz. (S7 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Status Quo Combustion: With potential changes affecting different aspects of his personal and professional life, Sheldon is forced to confront an uncertain future. (S7 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Last Walt: Claire supports Luke when his friend Walt dies. Phil takes Alex for some father-daughter bonding time, and Haley throws an unauthorised party. (S3 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Planes, Trains & Cars: The Dunphys want a new car and Phil makes a spontaneous purchase without Claire. Jay is determined to sort his high school reunion with Gloria and Manny. (S3 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Locomotion Reverberation: Leonard and Howard distract Sheldon with a trip to a historic railway when he slows their progress on the guidance system. (S10 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Allowance Evaporation: Amy is furious when she learns that Sheldon has shared intimate details of their relationship with his colleagues. (S10 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Comic-Con Conundrum: Cut off from his father's fortune, Raj appoints Sheldon to organise his finances. Penny considers joining the guys at Comic-Con. (S10 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Escape Hatch Identification: Leonard and Penny offer Sheldon's old room to Raj when he's forced to move out of his flat, leading to unexpected conflict. (S10 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Cinco de Mayo: When Jeffords becomes anxious about his upcoming lieutenant's exam, the squad hold the precinct's annual Halloween Heist on a new date. (S6 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sicko: Peralta and Boyle investigate a serial killer. Holt spars with his rival, Commissioner Kelly. Jeffords deals with complications after his recent exam. (S6 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa Gets the Blues: Lisa gets the yips and Bart is made to dress up and sing as Annie from the musical. They go to New Orleans to recover. (S29 Ep17/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Forgive and Regret: Grampa, thinking he's about to die, reveals a terrible secret. Can Homer forgive him? (S29 Ep18/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's rural retreat time, and a welcome romantic break for some. But rumours about a bride's behaviour spiral, and another bride learns a heartbreaking truth. (S10 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Celebration Reverberation: Sheldon and Howard plan birthday celebrations for Amy and Halley. Leonard is stressed by a Christmas letter from his brother. (S11 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Matrimonial Metric: Sheldon and Amy secretly test their friends, to work out who should be best man and maid of honour at their wedding. (S11 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Please Homer Don't Hammer 'Em: Marge discovers that she has a gift for carpentry, but has to use Homer as a cover in order to overcome prejudices against women builders. (S18 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror XVII: Homer ingests a blob from an asteroid; Bart enslaves a clay monster; and everyone thinks that aliens are invading. (S18 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Waverly Hills, 9-0-2-1-D'oh: The family rent a flat in the affluent Waverly Hills area so that Bart and Lisa can get into a good school. (S20 Ep19/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Won't Be Home for Christmas: When Moe convinces Homer to stay out late on Christmas Eve, Marge kicks him out of the house and he has to spend Christmas alone. (S26 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Supercruising: Life at Sea
E4Plus1.uk.description: The team sailing the Americas traverse the Panama Canal while passengers enjoy showstopping cakes. And in Europe, cruisers go whale watching near Tenerife. (Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox 2021
E4Plus1.uk.description: What do Britain's favourite TV viewers think of 2021's biggest shows, from Squid Game to Strictly and Line of Duty? Including the Siddiqui family, Giles and Mary, and Jenny and Lee.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash: Restoring Classics
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Paul Smith Mini / TY80: The team send their Paul Smith Mini in for a bit of designer tailoring by the team at Mini Sport. S7 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Austin Gipsy/Toyota MR2 Ferrari: Derek heads to Scotland in the mother of all rainstorms to pick up a Jaguar E-type and a rare MGC convertible. Plus, Dave extracts a rare Austin Gipsey from a lock up.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Jowett Javelin/Ford Escort: Derek dives into the lost Jowett marque, as a 1952 Javelin finds an unexpected home. Paul and Dave find a Ford Escort that's been untouched for 30 years. S1 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Bond Bug/Jag MK2: A 1970s Bond Bug three-wheeler divides opinion among Mathewsons customers, while a retired engineer reluctantly auctions off his father's treasured 60s Jaguar Mark 2. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Abandoned Engineering
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Drop: Exploring the Dew Drop Inn in New Orleans, a music mecca that dared to take on the authorities and paid the price, and Belgica Fort, built to defend an unlikely treasure. S10 Ep12

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: This World: Burma With Simon Reeve
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Simon Reeve ventures into Burma's highlands, where he attends a fire balloon festival, visits an elephant sanctuary, and goes in search of a rebel army. S1 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shopping from Home.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Moskovich/MGB GT: A Cold War Soviet classic goes under the hammer. Built like a tank, the Moskvitch gets few admirers for style, but finds a home with a fan of Eastern Bloc classics. S1 Ep6
